data.description: Centrally located ranch home near Town Center. Living Room and Dining Room combination with lots of natural light. Renovated in 2016. Upgrades include newer roof, windows, HVAC, water heater, hardwood flooring, remodeled tiled bath, kitchen cabinets, counter tops, lighting fixtures and newer vinyl wrap on the home. Bedroom with cedar walk in closet and bay window. Large laundry room which could support another bath. Floored attic space. Large 15x25 detached garage w/room above. Large white vinyl privacy fence w/car sized gate going back to the detached garage.  Easy access to interstates, bases, beach, shopping, and entertainment.
